 ***** Use string reference instead of string.

Q:1:  Write a program of Pattern searching and substring generation. Use proper directory structure /Package and modules for the function. 
Pattern Searching: 
		String= “Pankaj Chaudhary”		pattern=”Cha”
		Return= Pattern Found at index 7.

Substring generation:
		String= “pa”
		Substrings= [“p”, “a”, “pa”]

Q:2: Write a function to get desired output ?

Input :- Three Strings => str1 =  “jjdhid”  str2 = “ikjhjk”  str3 = “rtysgi”

Output :- One String => “itdsgk”  

Hint{
Even Position of Output String :- Suppose :-  d & k => d
Odd Position of Output String :-   d & k => k
(*Position starts from 0)
}
